---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Identity">
	<div class="bg-mesh"></div>
	<div class="bg-grid"></div>

	<section class="about-hero container animate-fade-in">
		<div class="hero-layout">
			<div class="hero-left">
				<span class="mono-label">// 004 // IDENTITY_CORE</span>
				<h1 class="page-title">THE_ <br/><span class="text-outline">TAQ_STORY</span></h1>
				<p class="page-subtitle">FROM A SPECIALIZED RESEARCH LAB TO A GLOBAL ENGINEERING POWERHOUSE, DEFINING THE NEXT ERA OF INDUSTRIAL-GRADE SOFTWARE SYSTEMS AND AI_INFRASTRUCTURE.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="about-content container">
		<div class="main-split">
			<article class="text-block animate-fade-in">
				<span class="mono-label">ORIGINS_01 // WORLDVIEW</span>
				<h2>GLOBAL_FOUNDATIONS</h2>
				<p>TAQ LAB IS A HIGH-PERFORMANCE ENGINEERING FIRM OPERATING AT THE INTERSECTION OF MODULAR ARCHITECTURE, AI_INFRASTRUCTURE, AND SPATIAL LOGIC. WE SPECIALIZE IN THE DEVELOPMENT OF RESILIENT SOFTWARE SYSTEMS AND ADVANCED INFERENCE OPTIMIZATION FOR GLOBAL ENTERPRISES.</p>
				<p>OUR MISSION IS TO BUILD INFRASTRUCTURE THAT IS NOT JUST FUNCTIONAL, BUT IMMUTABLE, SCALABLE, AND SECURE BY DESIGN. WE OPERATE AS A DECENTRALIZED COLLECTIVE OF ELITE ENGINEERS DEDICATED TO SYSTEMIC INTEGRITY.</p>
				<div class="philosophy-grid">
					<div class="phi-item glass-card">
						<span class="mono-label">P_01 // CORE</span>
						<h4>AI_INFRA_OPS</h4>
						<p>SCALABLE ARCHITECTURES DESIGNED TO POWER THE MOST DEMANDING INFERENCE WORKLOADS AT THE EDGE AND CORE.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="phi-item glass-card">
						<span class="mono-label">P_02 // SKILLS</span>
						<h4>ELITE_TRAINING</h4>
						<p>BRIDGING THE GAP BETWEEN THEORETICAL RESEARCH AND INDUSTRIAL-GRADE ENGINEERING EXECUTION THROUGH RIGOROUS BOOTCAMPS.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="phi-item glass-card">
						<span class="mono-label">P_03 // BASE</span>
						<h4>INTEGRITY_INDEX</h4>
						<p>SECURITY IS NOT AN ADD-ON; IT IS THE FUNDAMENTAL BASELINE OF EVERY LINE OF CODE WE COMMIT TO PRODUCTION.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</article>
			<aside class="stats-sidebar animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.2s">
				<div class="glass-card stat-card">
					<div class="stat">
						<span class="stat-number">2024</span>
						<span class="mono-label">INCEPTION_YEAR</span>
					</div>
					<div class="stat">
						<span class="stat-number">ELITE</span>
						<span class="mono-label">ENGINEERING_OPS</span>
					</div>
					<div class="stat">
						<span class="stat-number">GBL</span>
						<span class="mono-label">CORE_REACH</span>
					</div>
				</div>
			</aside>
		</div>

		<div class="vision-mission">
			<article class="glass-card vision-card animate-fade-in">
				<span class="mono-label">V_01 // VISION_PLAN</span>
				<h3>THE_FUTURE_STATE</h3>
				<p>TO BECOME THE GLOBAL STANDARD-BEARER FOR MODULAR ENGINEERING, AI_INFRASTRUCTURE, AND INFERENCE GOVERNANCE, POWERING THE MOST CRITICAL DIGITAL INFRASTRUCTURES.</p>
			</article>
			<article class="glass-card mission-card animate-fade-in" style="animation-delay: 0.1s">
				<span class="mono-label">V_02 // MISSION_DATA</span>
				<h3>THE_CORE_PURPOSE</h3>
				<p>TO PROVIDE GLOBAL ORGANIZATIONS WITH THE PRECISION TOOLS AND RIGOROUS RESEARCH NECESSARY TO NAVIGATE AI_ACCELERATED DELIVERY SAFELY.</p>
			</article>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="legal-assurance container">
		<article class="glass-card legal-card animate-fade-in">
			<span class="mono-label">REGULATORY // 01 // GLOBAL_COMPLIANCE</span>
			<h3>ENTITY_STATUS</h3>
			<p>TAQ LAB OPERATES UNDER RIGOROUS INTERNATIONAL COMPLIANCE STANDARDS. OUR LEGAL STATUS, OPERATIONAL FRAMEWORKS, AND DATA SOVEREIGNTY PROTOCOLS ARE MAINTAINED WITH THE HIGHEST DEGREE OF TRANSPARENCY FOR GLOBAL PARTNERS.</p>
			<div class="compliance-logos">
				<div class="logo-placeholder">GBL_ENTITY_ID</div>
				<div class="logo-placeholder">IDENTITY_VERIFIED</div>
				<div class="logo-placeholder">CORE_PROTO_ACK</div>
			</div>
		</article>
	</section>

	<style>
		.about-hero {
			padding: 15rem 0 10rem;
		}

		.page-title {
			font-size: clamp(4rem, 15vw, 10rem);
			margin: 2.5rem 0;
			line-height: 0.85;
			letter-spacing: -0.04em;
		}

		.page-subtitle {
			font-family: var(--font-mono);
			font-size: 0.95rem;
			color: var(--text-muted);
			max-width: 500px;
			letter-spacing: 0.05em;
			line-height: 1.8;
		}

		.about-content {
			padding: 6rem 0;
		}

		.main-split {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 3fr 2fr;
			gap: 8rem;
			margin-bottom: 10rem;
			align-items: start;
		}

		.text-block h2 {
			font-size: 3.5rem;
			margin: 2.5rem 0;
			letter-spacing: -0.04em;
		}

		.text-block p {
			font-family: var(--font-mono);
			font-size: 0.95rem;
			color: var(--text-muted);
			margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
			line-height: 1.8;
		}

		.philosophy-grid {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
			gap: 1.5rem;
			margin-top: 6rem;
		}

		.phi-item h4 {
			font-size: 1.4rem;
			margin: 1.5rem 0 1rem;
			letter-spacing: -0.02em;
		}

		.stat-card {
			display: flex;
			flex-direction: column;
			gap: 5rem;
			text-align: center;
			border-left: 1px solid var(--accent-primary);
			padding: 6rem 4rem;
		}

		.stat-number {
			font-size: 4rem;
			font-weight: 950;
			display: block;
			margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
			line-height: 1;
		}

		.vision-mission {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
			gap: 1.5rem;
			margin-bottom: 15rem;
		}

		.vision-mission h3 {
			font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
			margin: 2.5rem 0 1.5rem;
			letter-spacing: -0.02em;
			line-height: 1.1;
		}

		.vision-mission p {
			font-family: var(--font-mono);
			font-size: 0.95rem;
			color: var(--text-muted);
			line-height: 1.8;
		}

		.legal-assurance {
			padding-bottom: 15rem;
		}

		.legal-card {
			text-align: center;
			padding: 10rem 4rem;
		}

		.legal-card h3 {
			font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 3.5rem);
			margin: 2.5rem 0;
			letter-spacing: -0.02em;
		}

		.legal-card p {
			font-family: var(--font-mono);
			font-size: 1rem;
			color: var(--text-muted);
			max-width: 850px;
			margin: 0 auto 6rem;
			line-height: 1.8;
		}

		.compliance-logos {
			display: flex;
			justify-content: center;
			gap: 5rem;
			flex-wrap: wrap;
		}

		.logo-placeholder {
			font-family: var(--font-mono);
			font-size: 0.8rem;
			font-weight: 700;
			color: var(--text-muted);
			padding: 1.5rem 3rem;
			border: 1px dashed var(--border-color);
		}

		@media (max-width: 992px) {
			.main-split {
				grid-template-columns: 1fr;
				gap: 5rem;
			}
			.vision-mission {
				grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			}
			.stat-card {
				border-left: none;
				border-top: 1px solid var(--accent-primary);
				padding-top: 5rem;
			}
		}

		@media (max-width: 768px) {
			.page-title {
				font-size: 3.5rem;
			}
			.philosophy-grid {
				grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			}
			.text-block h2 {
				font-size: 2.2rem;
			}
			.stat-card {
				gap: 3rem;
				padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
			}
			.stat-number {
				font-size: 3rem;
			}
			.legal-card {
				padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
			}
			.compliance-logos {
				gap: 2rem;
			}
		}
	</style>
</Layout>
